div.p:
VII. Have I not been Unchast, in my Acts, my Thoughts, my Words; 
   〈◊〉
 or been a Companion of the Fools, that are so?

1. I. The Apostles place or station in the He of Patmo: (now Patina) neer the Shore of the AEgean Sea, Rev. 13. 1. looking Eastward toward Ephesus and Jerusalem;
Zech. 14. 4. as you may suppose: Act. 1. 〈…〉
because our Lord is represented standing upon Mount Olivet in that day. Where (in Speculo Visionis) in a Visionary Glass, he beholds with great attention what the Angel presented to him.
